		padding: 0;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}
	.charsRanks>div:first-child{
		margin-left:0;
	}
	.charsRanks>div:last-child{
		margin-right:0;
	}
	.border-dd{
		border: 1px solid #DDDDDD;
